{"tid":174533,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟一個人人格低成點先會一上車就第一時間搵位坐","createTime":"2017-03-27T01:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T14:06:32.000Z","uid":73429,"like":2,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4123d095ab08fa469628fe2a06e85a96d6e166bc","tid":174533,"uid":73429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T01:01:40.000Z","msg":"撇除身體唔舒服或不便因素，永遠上車都唔係等人先落晒後上車。一上車，第一時間就係搵位坐，企下好似會死咁<br />\n利申，從來唔坐，除非啲位多到無人坐"},{"pid":"9da943c57463d4b178b0a62a68ffbe3853856560","tid":174533,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T01:15:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">屯門搭到柴灣一上車就坐算唔算人格低劣呀屌你老母</span>"},{"pid":"5ead87f535633e9ef1cd1938bbba50fc234d81a9","tid":174533,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T01:18:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撇除身體唔舒服或不便因素，永遠上車都唔係等人先落晒後上車。一上車，第一時間就係搵位坐，企下好似會死咁<br />\n利申，從來唔坐，除非啲位多到無人坐</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母，咁啲位拎黎做乜鳩呀仆街"},{"pid":"6f40cbc7455c890730f66c9a0dc34e7ebb2e5fee","tid":174533,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T01:19:40.000Z","msg":"樓主呢啲真係生岀嚟俾人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係唔係啲位俾曬廢老坐就happy end<br />\n我有俾錢㗎屌你老母"},{"pid":"9207bb0ee1f31bfb52c3ad4ebd74390eb85ad18c","tid":174533,"uid":20269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T01:30:25.000Z","msg":"你咁唔想坐就行喇仆街<br />\n搭乜春野車"},{"pid":"7f5dfa18a105fc99fe93eea536e3590f204e5aff","tid":174533,"uid":58201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T01:48:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來座位唔係拎黎比人坐 <br />\n係咪比樓主你拎黎打飛機扮清高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee988fcbf1f76c75f7ae46498c898e422c332c84","tid":174533,"uid":95478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T01:54:37.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"3ef31c435e8cb947985320f9ac9ab6df28078473","tid":174533,"uid":81345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T01:54:59.000Z","msg":"究竟樓主人格低成點先會出世？？"},{"pid":"0870a7be555b2857a98c1b82cdd88a16151b0120","tid":174533,"uid":15427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T01:55:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撇除身體唔舒服或不便因素，<span style=\"color: red;\">永遠上車都唔係等人先落晒後上車</span>。一上車，第一時間就係搵位坐，企下好似會死咁<br />\n利申，從來唔坐，除非啲位多到無人坐</blockquote><br />\n紅字為重點？"},{"pid":"def8293ff6cfacdbd12e028664147a13dcce46cf","tid":174533,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T01:58:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  Agger ,  等睇玻璃心批鬥樓主"},{"pid":"eefb32efcd816947ed1fcb9762cb16c5ba4b026e","tid":174533,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T01:59:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撇除身體唔舒服或不便因素，永遠上車都唔係等人先落晒後上車。一上車，第一時間就係搵位坐，企下好似會死咁<br />\n利申，從來唔坐，除非啲位多到無人坐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n夠竟人格低成點先會一入餐廳就搵位坐?<br />\n<br />\n撇除身體唔舒服或不便因素，永遠入餐廳都唔係等人食哂走哂先。一入餐廳，第一時間就係買餐搵位坐，企下好似會死咁<br />\n利申，從來唔坐，除非啲位多到無人坐"},{"pid":"325a32aa6fdc8f95b398449594706a9acb8e8d4e","tid":174533,"uid":17776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:00:41.000Z","msg":"同廢老搶位？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/27/100015_3773eaf8b225b0fbf96e650349c24b8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F27%2F100015_3773eaf8b225b0fbf96e650349c24b8b.jpg&h=5b7c7759&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96ab773f216d2bb7b3f7617c4f3fbb42276d77ce","tid":174533,"uid":12362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:02:14.000Z","msg":"一上車搵位坐同唔等落晒就上車應該分開評論，前者好難話有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e25335a704078ac2b86bcfb0c1acdd6ed8dd6a","tid":174533,"uid":73429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:12:33.000Z","msg":"呢個post完美演繹低劣人格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"068f880a604921b6c35a62c34100405001ffc9be","tid":174533,"uid":73429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:13:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">屯門搭到柴灣一上車就坐算唔算人格低劣呀屌你老母</span></blockquote><br />\n你屯門可以直達柴灣你咪坐囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8f6ae55e3772f5ba53eab121be784ea53ab1a7","tid":174533,"uid":73429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:13:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一上車搵位坐同唔等落晒就上車應該分開評論，前者好難話有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔等入落晒就入十之八九都係驚無位坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"662c742a823c0376e359f7177a547ab33ddeda91","tid":174533,"uid":73429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:14:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>撇除身體唔舒服或不便因素，永遠上車都唔係等人先落晒後上車。一上車，第一時間就係搵位坐，企下好似會死咁<br />\n利申，從來唔坐，除非啲位多到無人坐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n夠竟人格低成點先會一入餐廳就搵位坐?<br />\n<br />\n撇除身體唔舒服或不便因素，永遠入餐廳都唔係等人食哂走哂先。一入餐廳，第一時間就係買餐搵位坐，企下好似會死咁<br />\n利申，從來唔坐，除非啲位多到無人坐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用餐廳黎做例子比較，真係得閣下嘅智商先做得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8bedc9ae18ce8a221fb6528b3813eb22c738354","tid":174533,"uid":19728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:16:36.000Z","msg":"咁啲櫈要嚟做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c685729f893cc6b7de96f1481c0d554ee9c37feb","tid":174533,"uid":73429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:17:29.000Z","msg":"好多廢中廢老入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一上車即刻搵位坐，除左人格低就係啲廢中廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb01997d4de857ad1f8cd38363ac05c6846cfb4","tid":174533,"ui